query:
INSERT INTO asset
            (
                owner_id,

                item_id,
                location_id,
                type_id,

                location_flag,
                location_type,
                quantity,
                is_singleton,
                is_blueprint_copy
            )
            SELECT $1, * FROM UNNEST(
                $2::BIGINT[],
                $3::BIGINT[],
                $4::INTEGER[],
                $5::VARCHAR[],
                $6::VARCHAR[],
                $7::INTEGER[],
                $8::BOOLEAN[],
                $9::BOOLEAN[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (item_id)
            DO UPDATE SET
                location_id = EXCLUDED.location_id,
                location_flag = EXCLUDED.location_flag,
                quantity = EXCLUDED.quantity,
                is_singleton = EXCLUDED.is_singleton
